SELECT  case when SUBSTRING(RawData,1,4) = '' then null else SUBSTRING(RawData,1,4) end as FlightNumber

, case when SUBSTRING(RawData,11,1) = '' then null else SUBSTRING(RawData,11,1) end as FlightLegCode
,cast(concat(SUBSTRING(RawData,17,4),SUBSTRING(RawData,15,2),SUBSTRING(RawData,13,2)) as date) as OperationDay
, case when SUBSTRING(RawData,21,4) = '' then null else SUBSTRING(RawData,21,4) end as ArrivalStation
, case when SUBSTRING(RawData,25,4) = '' then null else SUBSTRING(RawData,25,4) end as DepartureStation

select FlightCrewFlightID
,substring(Names,1,2) as Position 
,substring(Names,4,1) as CrewPax 
,substring(Names,5,1) as Role 
,substring(Names,8,8) as ID 
,substring(Names,16,30) as Name 
,TFileName
,TCreatedId
,TLoadDate
from (
SELECT FlightCrewFlightID,Names, Crew, TFileName, TCreatedId ,TLoadDate from 
(select 
SUBSTRING(RawData,1,4) FlightCrewFlightID
, SUBSTRING(RawData,62,45) as Name1
, SUBSTRING(RawData,107,45) as Name2
, SUBSTRING(RawData,152,45) as Name3
, SUBSTRING(RawData,197,45) as Name4
, SUBSTRING(RawData,242,45) as Name5
, SUBSTRING(RawData,287,45) as Name6
, SUBSTRING(RawData,332,45) as Name7
, SUBSTRING(RawData,377,45) as Name8
, SUBSTRING(RawData,422,45) as Name9
, SUBSTRING(RawData,422,45) as Name10
, SUBSTRING(RawData,467,45) as Name11
, SUBSTRING(RawData,512,45) as Name12
, SUBSTRING(RawData,557,45) as Name13
, SUBSTRING(RawData,602,45) as Name14
, SUBSTRING(RawData,647,45) as Name15
, SUBSTRING(RawData,692,45) as Name16
, SUBSTRING(RawData,737,45) as Name17
, SUBSTRING(RawData,782,45) as Name18
, SUBSTRING(RawData,827,45) as Name19
, SUBSTRING(RawData,872,45) as Name20
,TFileName
,TCreatedId
,TLoadDate
 FROM [BcAdfAims].[FlightCrew_Stage]
 ) p
UNPIVOT
    (Names for Crew in 
        (Name1,Name2,Name3,Name4,Name5,Name6,Name7,Name8,Name9,Name10,
        Name11,Name12,Name13,Name14,Name15,Name16,Name17,Name18,Name19,Name20) ) as unpvt
) final
where substring(Names,16,30) <>''
